flavor_text_entries.red:
A legendary bird
POKéMON that is
said to appear to doomed people who
are lost in icy
mountains.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
A legendary bird
POKéMON that is
said to appear to doomed people who
are lost in icy
mountains.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
A legendary bird
POKéMON. It
freezes water that is contained
in winter air and
makes it snow.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
The magnificent,
seemingly translu­
cent wings of this legendary bird
POKéMON are said
to be made of ice.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
One of the legen­
dary bird POKéMON,
it chills moisture in the atmosphere
to create snow
while flying.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
Legendary bird
POKéMON. As it
flies through the sky, it cools the
air, causing snow
to fall.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
ARTICUNO is a legendary bird POKéMON
that can control ice.
The flapping of its wings chills the air. As a result, it is said that when this
POKéMON flies, snow will fall.

with permafrost.
